Class CallableCharInsertion

Callable<CallableCharInsertion>
public class CallableCharInsertion extends AbstractCallableBinary<CallableCharInsertion>
Define a call HTTP to the server, require the associated url, character position and bit. Opcodes represent the differences between the reference page, and the resulting page.
